{"tid":2212661,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過突然覺得對屋企人好內疚","createTime":"2020-09-22T03:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T11:23:04.000Z","uid":805,"like":292,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c0993493bcb56d3ff2526e1a2514b706a85c0bcc","tid":2212661,"uid":805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T03:57:14.000Z","msg":"我就係同阿媽咁啱係同一日生日既 老豆早死 咁阿媽同阿婆就由中學照顧到我而家大學畢業 期間靠老母打份半全職既工同埋以前留落既積蓄過活 咁照顧我日常生活都照顧得我好好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁早幾日阿媽就買左三隻好大隻既瀨尿蝦返黎同我一齊食諗住一齊慶祝下生日<br />\n<br />\n 睇到佢好興奮 托住隻瀨尿蝦係手同佢手臂比 係咁叫我影相 果下見到唔知點解好心酸 因爲老豆未死果陣佢係少奶奶 唔洗做 同時都唔會有呢啲反應 所以佢既興奮反應真係令我好心酸<br />\n<br />\n見到佢笑果陣隻眼尾啲皺紋開始明顯 突然意識到阿媽開始老了 果下即刻眼濕濕自己行返入房<br />\n<br />\n諗起佢好多年都冇食過好嘢 用既電話都係好多年前既basic model 之類 男人老狗諗諗下呢啲諗到哩埋係被竇度喊到成隻狗咁<br />\n<br />\n咁我同老母都係一樣唔係好識表達自己感情既人黎 有時會嘈到好大 但我都知道老母好錫我<br />\n<br />\n原本我仲諗住生日換張rtx3080比自己 但諗起自己比阿媽生日都係比1000蚊就即刻覺得自己好衰 於是我即刻二話不說上網訂左部ipad比老母諗住比個驚喜佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寧願自己生日唔買嘢都想買嘢比老母 等佢開心下<br />\n<br />\n下年佢五十歲準備請佢去龍景軒食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路係公司廁所打呢段嘢一路打到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果屋企人好錫你既 記得平時都對佢地好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fee84ab085e8f065f7a972ab65a5a274e2408f0","tid":2212661,"uid":214644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c417af045553e5fe3dfc0d53842fa15ce168506","tid":2212661,"uid":53844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T03:59:00.000Z","msg":"我會架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07657d7c9c8ea5f98ea14124c12af68fac3732e","tid":2212661,"uid":23431,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:01:51.000Z","msg":"佢最好既生日禮物就係佢生日你出世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd60fe064069d1154d3bfe4168161055efa17e55","tid":2212661,"uid":14606,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:01:59.000Z","msg":"我都想對媽媽好d 但已經無機會啦 <br />\n你有機會既 就對佢好d 唔好令自己後悔"},{"pid":"510c76154d7d0b8f14370f0f68de06fadd08832b","tid":2212661,"uid":85225,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:47:47.000Z","msg":"我都試過，因為失戀喺屋企係咁喊，有幾次俾屋企人見到，佢哋係咁聽我喊住咁呻，係咁叫我唔好喊，我阿媽仲聽到眼濕濕同我一齊喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果一刻真係覺得自己好不孝，會問自己點解會曾經覺得另一半重要過屋企人，點解明知唔值得都要咁難過，仲要搞到屋企人同自己一齊傷心難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff36f502ae459bddd292ae255fb2565c2fff42a","tid":2212661,"uid":805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0545f76642c79891f0cb1c103ac1fa2d5a982891","tid":2212661,"uid":320293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22109d138e0d492fdfea00b98691afa5ea36c31f","tid":2212661,"uid":302633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:15:56.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e34b481b647216c1db3f3df8a2e971c99daa9a8","tid":2212661,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T08:50:33.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放唔低面子"},{"pid":"3c9dd9179a716fdb3f1edb8b23b2da38471cc3d2","tid":2212661,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:29:17.000Z","msg":"有，20幾歲人好撚失敗...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6f19fed72d221c63a9bbc46220d5ce8817435d","tid":2212661,"uid":308450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb685fc6a84f6cabbbb51916f43e94f14ed69514","tid":2212661,"uid":44180,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3925ecd3f883f06e3d52da69d06079265218cc9f","tid":2212661,"uid":203701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3431b8465b81031771a87beca953af0e5d3d407","tid":2212661,"uid":58201,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T11:06:10.000Z","msg":"有 有時諗起自己咁垃圾 仲心酸內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ceb18f9ef4bb3d2895668b0c715974ab69c8fe","tid":2212661,"uid":94215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T11:12:41.000Z","msg":"黎緊比心機做人,腳踏實地做野報答下媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將來做D咩緊要事之前,諗一諗做左之後敢唔敢大大聲同啊媽講,唔敢嘅話就唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"dc23fd3912ab2ae262c1621c6d45642f3ea7d156","tid":2212661,"uid":114046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T11:14:14.000Z","msg":"諗諗吓自己都冇乜點對過屋企人好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},